
{help f_invchi2tail:English Version}
{hline}
{* *! version 1.1.1  02mar2015}{...}
    {cmd:invchi2tail(}{it:df}{cmd:,}{it:p}{cmd:)}
{p2colset 8 22 22 2}{...}
{p2col: 描述：}这是 {cmd:chi2tail()} 的反函数：如果
	{cmd:chi2tail(}{it:df}{cmd:,}x{cmd:)} = {it:p}，则
	{cmd:invchi2tail(}{it:df}{cmd:,}{it:p}{cmd:)} = {it:x}{p_end}
{p2col: 定义域 {it:df}:}2e-10 到 2e+17（可能是非整数值){p_end}
{p2col: 定义域 {it:p}:}0 到 1{p_end}
{p2col: 值域：}0 到 8e+307{p_end}
{p2colreset}{...}